    "body": "I ended up reimplementing the interface on top of regular mutexes https://github.com/servo/servo/blob/master/components/util/remutex.rs. The main use case is data structures that are reentrant but not thread-safe, and use interior mutability. In our case that was IPC channels, but you can do similar examples with cells.\n",
